Remember... that time... when I faced the
Minotaur...\n<Serena>

Lady Erika... even more battered than I am now,
she still stood up...!!\n<Serena>

No matter how defiled... how wounded, she never
gave up and confronted the formidable enemy!!!\n<Serena>

Am I going to falter now, after vowing to
protect...? Serena. Fuoco. R. Brillante. D. La.
Gratia!\n<Serena>

Right in front of me... within reach, my radiance
is seeking help...!!\n<Serena>

...What I need is not power, not the power to
oppress others...!\n<Serena>

A heart of compassion to think of someone and
reach out a hand...\n<Serena>

And then... a strong, unbreakable heart like Lady
Erika's!!\n<Serena>

That's right. As long as this heartbeat... this
sound doesn't cease... I must stand up!\n<Serena>

With my heartbeat... with my feelings as my
sustenance...!!\n<Serena>
Cloak my body and become my shield... Affabile!!\n<Serena>

To destroy the wicked being that dares to tarnish
my shine!!\n<Serena>
Come now... spawn of magic not of human kind...\n<Serena>

Whether my heart will be devoured or your body
will decay...\n<Serena>
Let us decide the outcome!!\n<Serena>
神に祈る
